description:
&lt;h2&gt;Recovery Associate/HCSW&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;A vacancy has now become available within our busy Endoscopy Unit at the Queen Alexandra Hospital University Trust, Portsmouth.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are a highly motivated team running five full time Endoscopy suites, and an unsedated nurse-led satellite unit at the Gosport War Memorial. The post holder will be expected to be mobile across both sites.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Our services include an ever increasing number of specialised therapeutic and diagnostic procedures.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The main responsibility of this post will be as a vital member of the Nursing team, which involves caring for patients before during and after their procedures. This can be a physically demanding and challenging role but is very rewarding for the right candidate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post holder will be expected to work alongside the registered Nurses in delivering high level nursing care to patients in all areas of the department, including covering the Gosport Unit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you are motivated, enthusiastic and a self confident person, possessing a good sense of humour then you may be ideally suited to join our friendly team within the Endoscopy Unit. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The applicant does not require previous endoscopy experience as all training will be given.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Working pattern - Monday to Sunday, 08.00 to 22.00 (working pattern may be negotiable to suit successful applicant, and may be subject to change as the service develops).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;For further information, discussion and/or visit please contact Natalie Tolfree on 02392 286000 x 3406.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date: 18/11/2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
